snippet.title: Outland Odyssey: Game Development Update
snippet.description:
After a series of pre-launch tests of our highly anticipated RPG - Outland Odyssey, Project SEED is proud to announce our very first Strix Beta Release, kicking off on June 6, 2022. Months of work have built up to this, and we couldn’t be more excited to share it with you. 

This first ever beta release takes a vital role in determining the long-term success of our game as it has always been community-driven and we constantly seek valuable feedback from our own community, the very players of Outland Odyssey in the future. Ultimately, this release is the long-awaited final run to improve and refine our game in the best possible way before its official launch.
